Choose one of the following: BIO111, BIO161.

One course from each of the following GE areas must be completed: A1, A2, A3, C1, C2, C3, C4, C1-C4 elective, D1, D2, D3, D5, and F. C4, D5, and F should be taken only after Junior standing is reached (90 units). 52 units GE required. Refer to online catalog for GE course selection and Graduation Writing Requirement (GWR). Note: If KINE 255 or 260 is selected, USCP is fulfilled. If KINE 250 is selected, USCP can be fulfilled by some, but not all, courses in the following GE areas: C3, C4, D1, D3, D5, or F.
